  "title": "Accounts Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Full scope of Accounts Payable and Receivable</p></li><li><p>Cash Flow forecast for assigned Project</p></li><li><p>Prepare Cost Management Reports</p></li><li><p>Assist in monthly, quarterly and financial reporting</p></li><li><p>Assist to prepare schedules and reporting to IBU / Japan HQ</p></li><li><p>Assist in Suppliers’ Statement of Account reconciliation</p></li><li><p>Assist in any other accounting functions as required by HOD</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Recognized Diploma in Accountancy or equivalent</p></li><li><p>Min 2 years of relevant working experience in similar position</p></li><li><p>Proficient in Microsoft Excel and Pivot Table</p></li><li><p>Knowledge of other relevant computer applications would be an advantage</p></li><li><p>Ability to manage multiple tasks and meet deadlines</p></li><li><p>Effective communication in the workplace</p></li><li><p>Work Location: Project site office based in Changi</p></li></ul>",
